      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im 54 and i've had asthma since i was a kid. lately i've been feeling kinda weird... like i get out of breath just walking from my bedroom to the kitchen. is this just me getting older or should i be worried about my inhaler?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
