      "content": "It's definitely not just \"getting older,\" but it's also not a crisis, so don't panic. Your breathing issues are likely a sign your current asthma management needs a tune-up, not a complete overhaul. I strongly recommend you schedule an appointment with your primary care physician to discuss this. They can adjust your current medication regimen to better control your symptoms.",
